J_0(n)
\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}|J_0(n)| < \rm C
\lim\limits_{n \to\infty} J_0(n) = 0
J_0(n)\sim\sqrt{\frac 2{n\pi}}\cos(n-\pi/4)
|J_0(n)|\sim\sqrt{\frac 2{n\pi}}|\cos(n-\pi/4)|=:a_n
b_n:=\sqrt{\frac{\pi}2}a_n
\sum_{n>0}\frac 1{\sqrt n}
\sum_{n>0}\frac{\sin (2n)}{\sqrt n}
\sum_{n>0}b_n
\sum_{n=0}^{+\infty}|J_0(n)|
2b_n\geq\frac 2{\sqrt n}\cos^2\left(n-\frac{\pi}4\right)=\frac 1{\sqrt n}\left(1+\cos\left(2n-\frac{\pi}2\right)\right)=\frac{1-\sin(2n)}{\sqrt n}\geq 0.
